notesStmt.note: Poleman writes, R̥gvedasaṁhitā with padakrama notation.
Written 13-16 lines per leaf. Accented in red. Very few corrections in the margins.
Title page reads Idam yugapat saṁhitā padamiśrita kramasya pustakaṁ. Idam pustakaṁ prathamāṣṭakam kramasya.
tan mājiyatvā pariśodhanīyam kopann kuryāt khalu lekhanasya.

msItem.title: R̥gveda
msItem.colophon: Colophon: iti prathamāṣṭake aṣṭamah adhyāyaḥ samāptam. Samvat 1716 mārgaśīrṣa śuddha trayodaśīkāśyām idam pustakaṁ punyastam kśṇivāsī ṭemkālopa nāmaka dvārkā bhaṭṭa suta bāhu bhaṭṭena likhitaṁ savritaṁ svārtam paramȧrtham ca. aṣṭadoṣāśruti viśrama adhyāyah yad arthahinam likhitaṁ mayā adyā.
